Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–做好掩护  –迪莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Brace yourselves! - Disa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有座火山苏醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A fire-mountain awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地动山摇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ground-shakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着大地之骨一路蔓延\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it spread through the bones of the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁了我们的矿井\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}collapsing our sun-shafts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们种植作物的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our ability to grow crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些戒指的力量将超越矮人或人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These Rings will be beyond any power yet devised
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所能生成的任何力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by Dwarf, or Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些戒指将是力量之戒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They shall be Rings of Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以治愈你们的山脉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Power to heal your mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你父亲献上拯救王国的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bringing your father a means of saving his kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许正好能赢回他对你的尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}might be just the way to earn back his respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至你的继承资格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps, even your inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚是在羞辱我父亲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you just insult my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再敢说女王的不是 身体有恙的就会是你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You speak ill of the Queen again, it'll be you suffers an infirmity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说得够清楚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have I made myself plain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen of lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不配治国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's unfit to rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在临终之前 国王对我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His dying words, the King spoke to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说一切就是从这个开始 她听取了建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and said it was from this... she took counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗精灵之石左右了你们的女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This Elf-stone is your queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–安静  –这颗帕蓝提尔是我的 我们需要它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Silence! - The palantír is mine. We need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人凶手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑魔法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dark magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉宗...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉宗...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的至高王认为 矮人不配拥有这种力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your High King believes the Dwarves to be unworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 他禁止再打造任何戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, he has forbidden the forging of any more Rings at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没时间耗费唇舌 说服他谁值得帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have not the time to bandy words about, convincing him who is worthy of aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告诉至高王我将关闭熔炉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am telling him that I am closing up the forge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要对至高王说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would lie to your High King?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在争取时间完成我们的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would grant us the space to complete our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃瑞吉安那种力量 我无法信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This power in Eregion, I don't trust it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told me once,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵的命运是由 比我们更有智慧的存在决定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the fate of Elves is decided by wiser minds than our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图扭转 试图逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That to try and alter it, to try and cheat death,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会导致更大的灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}might lead to an even greater catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一你是对的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if you were right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥克大军进军精灵王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A legion of Orcs have marched into Elvish lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是通往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gather it leads to--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃瑞吉安 大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eregion, my liege.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的大军前往魔多之前 要让至高王知道这消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Word of this must reach the High King before our host sails for Mordor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去林顿 我会尽力拖延他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get to Lindon. I will occupy them as long as I am able.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德 拿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it, Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一颗星照耀着我们相遇的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A star shines on the hour of our meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}指环王:力量之戒\N第二季第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 这边请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所见 我们正尝试挖一个新矿井\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you can see, we're attempting to dig a new access-shaft,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让阳光照射进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to try to reach the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但目前为止我们所有努力 只让山脉变得更不稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, but thus far, our every effort has only made the mountain more unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿那把十字镐 挖这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在这里浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 怎么了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something the matter, sire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 一切很快会好起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, all is shortly to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dig here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 那是基础墙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sire. That's a foundation wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–伤到的话... –你是在教我怎么挖掘吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take it down-- - Are you explaining Delve-craft to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖这里就对了 照我说的做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is where we are meant to dig. Now do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把斧头给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me your axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–父王... –斧头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Father-- - Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Narvi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下班了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... Shift's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–太好了 –可不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's good. - Tell me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 不觉得最好停下来喘口气吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sire. Don't you think you'd better stop for some air?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要的不是空气 是阳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not air we need, it's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sire! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我叫你挖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next time I order you to dig,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给我挖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一 二 三 四 挖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜那些住在上面的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pity those who dwell above.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是太阳的奴隶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slaves to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被日出日落永无止境的节奏所束缚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chained to its ceaseless rhythm of waking and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在卡扎督姆 我们挣脱太阳的专制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Khazad-d?m, we are free of its tyranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 我们引光入洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, we bring the sun to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 我们的山城\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At last, it is daybreak once more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次迎来了黎明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in our mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡扎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khazad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,督姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D?m!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵和矮人携手合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dwarves and Elves working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说这是不可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was said to be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的合作造就了这个奇迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But our cooperation has achieved this wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 我们着手全新的梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And today, we embark upon a new dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们的友谊铭刻在石头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to enshrine our friendship in stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Narvi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳维的高光时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Narvi's big moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Behold...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林之门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Doors of Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们山城全新的西门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The new West-gate of our mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚不可摧 只在月光下显现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unbreachable. Visible only by moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口令守护 只有朋友才知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And guarded by a password, known only to friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住了 工匠们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, take note, smiths,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好盯着这位纳维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watch Narvi very closely while he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只因为他是技术高超的艺术家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not only because he is a masterful artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是恶名昭彰的小偷 可别弄丢了珠宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's also a notorious thief. Do not let any jewels go missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 捞捞他的口袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, try checking his pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬精灵和矮人之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To a lasting friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的友谊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}between Elves and Dwarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你们的热情款待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hospitality's much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太长了吗 我的致词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too much? My remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝过你尽量简短\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I encouraged you to keep it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得你有说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not recall you saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讲话你不一定在听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you do not always listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦你有自己的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once you have an idea set in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我应该多说点的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Truth is, I should've spoken longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢一下你的贡献\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To credit your contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在没心情庆祝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I find it difficult to stay festive,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔多崛起影响最深的那些人 还在受苦受难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when those most affected by Mordor's rise are still suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为人类打造戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rings for Men?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没提到戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not say anything about Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的手段 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a game you play, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他人心中播下种子 再说服他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sowing seeds in others' minds and then convincing them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果实是他们自己的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the fruit is of their own thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们的想法一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought our minds were as one in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改变主意了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you had a change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是属于矮人的夜晚 来吧 我们明天再讨论人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a night for Dwarves. Come. We shall speak of Men tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁可现在讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would prefer to speak of them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的许多苦难 都是他们自己造成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much of the misery of Men is of their own making.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还听说当初是南方人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I have been informed that it was the Men of the Southlands
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助阿达尔进行征服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who aided Adar in his conquest in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一部分人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的许多人已经有了新家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many of the rest have already been given new homes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的同类伸出援手 来自努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by their own kind, from Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去过努门诺尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever been to Númenor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却支离破碎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But fractured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在荣耀与毁灭之间摆荡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ever teetering between glory and ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fear Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比中洲其他地方都危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than any land in Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我们的戒指 能让那里稳定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had hoped our Rings might make her stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让人类拥有这种戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cannot give Rings to Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐化的风险太大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The risk of corruption is simply too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我们解决了什么问题 可能远远不及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever problems we might solve will be nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们制造的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}against those we could create.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 人类是很脆弱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. Men are capable of great frailty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而当黑暗降临时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when the darkness falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有人站出来绽放光芒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there are always some who rise forth and shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃雅仁迪尔 图奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}E?rendil, Tuor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拉希尔之子贝伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beren, son of Barahir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exactly what are you proposing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们挑选值得信任的人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We find Men we can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最聪慧 最高尚 最纯洁的心灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The wisest, the most noble, the purest of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从努门诺尔到鲁恩 我们选出九名持戒人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From Númenor to Rh?n, we identify nine Ring-bearers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌管九个人类王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the nine greatest mortal kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵三戒相当完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The perfection of the Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三倍的完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thrice perfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三次锻造 能造出九个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For our third forging, we will make nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 我们成就了伟大功业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have accomplished great things, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要试图超越能力范围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us not tempt failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以免招致失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by allowing our reach to exceed our grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我的答案是拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry. My answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量之戒已经完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Rings of Power are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用道歉 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need not apologize. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己打造那九戒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shall make the Nine myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看过吗 在我国西部海域彼端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever seen it? Across our western seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃瑞西亚的白塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The white tower of Eress?a...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往不死之地的大门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the very gateway to the Undying Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有最锐利的双眼看得到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only the keenest eye can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要从美尼尔塔玛山顶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And only from the peak of the Meneltarma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想精灵是刻意竖立在那里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I reckon the Elves placed it there on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样每次日落都在提醒我们 我们的岁月终将结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that every sunset serves as a reminder that our days must end
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的却不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and theirs will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我们爬得多高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That no matter how high we climb,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些东西我们永远无法企及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some things will be forever withheld from our grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,权杖现在是你的了 父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Scepter is now in yours, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还不够高吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that not high enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子都以为够高了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All my life, I believed it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,权杖掌握在你手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Scepter is what you make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的纪元即将来临 父亲 让我们迎接它吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Age of Men is upon us, Father. Let us take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们打造您心目中的努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us build the Númenor you have always seen in your mind's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在你母亲怀里时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once, when you were at her breast,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾预言你会有不好的下场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your mother prophesied that you would come to ill ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我即将交给你的任务做出成绩来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impress me in the task that I am about to place upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的话 我只好另找他处利用你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fail to do so, and I shall have to find other places to make use of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉宗...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听听他们的呼声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面还有别的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are other voices out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蓝迪尔说在旧城区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Valandil tells me that in the Old Quarter,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日夜都有人为你祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}prayers ascend night and day for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为他们的女王祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For their Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令给我们 我们能导正错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Command us all and together we can put this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–海卫队仍效忠于你 –埃兰迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The Sea-Guard is still loyal to you. - Elendil--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–我们可以一起战斗 –埃兰迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Together we can fight. - Elendil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你 让我再次敞开心扉 重拾忠贞派之路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was you, who opened my heart again to the way of The Faithful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发誓要继续效忠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We swore to keep serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要坐以待毙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, you wish to be still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任由狼群舔拭摇篮吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while the wolves are licking the cradle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么 在帕蓝提尔里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you see? In the palantír.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失魂落魄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑着马从城里去...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Riding from the city to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know not where.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你没看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you did not see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–看到什么  –或许命运改变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- See what? - Perhaps it's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是每场战斗都要打才能赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not every battle must be fought to be won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时保持内心平静就是最大的胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes maintaining stillness of heart is the greatest victory of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个人最极致的信念之举\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the greatest act of faith one can perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多年以来 我在帕蓝提尔里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For years, that palantír
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看到我们岛国的衰败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has shown me only our island's downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当你触碰它时 那景象就消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when you touched it, that vision was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转而踏上新的道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Changed to a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉宗掌权是那条道路的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pharaz?n's kingship is a part of that path.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要求我下令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have asked for my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我下令了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now it is given.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论他们怎么压迫你 无论他们想夺走什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter how hard they push you, no matter what they try and take,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝不能危及努门诺尔的新命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you must not jeopardize Númenor's new destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要在暴风眼深处保持冷静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must remain the calm at the storm's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回你的船上去 船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go back to your ship, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–你是自愿的吗  –对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You render it willingly? - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不再是海卫队员了 去吧 下一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're no longer a Sea-Guard. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Line up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the meaning of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要被认定效忠摄政女王 就会被剥夺军衔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone deemed loyal to the Queen-regent has been stripped of rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁授权的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On whose authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉没早点告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I'd hoped to tell you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔札加尔大人 打算以叛国罪起诉你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord Belzagar wanted the lot of you charged with treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你因为推翻女王获得晋升\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet, overthrowing a queen has earned you a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢把我的悲痛 贬低成卑微的野心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How dare you reduce my grief to petty ambition?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥瑞尔窥视精灵之石害死了我哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My brother is dead because Míriel peeped into an Elf-stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘲笑神圣之物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mock that which is sacred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘲笑的是荒谬之举\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mock that which is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔-法拉宗是你的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ar-Pharaz?n is your king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受吧 父亲 我求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Accept it, Father. I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走上的路相当险恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are walking a treacherous path.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你走上的路如履海水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yours is made of seawater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意脚下每一步 海水深不见底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take care to keep your feet beneath you, it's a long way to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–好了吗  –都在这里了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you ready? - Is everything there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–对 –下一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. - Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别动 都同艘船的 搜他身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all there. This is all from the same. Check him up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–记下来 –是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列份清单 方便记录
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭送船长离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain leaving deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在不是什么船长了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's nobody's captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说的没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–谢谢船长 –维拉保佑你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, Captain. - The Valar protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–谢谢船长 –谢谢船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, Captain. - Thank you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–维拉保佑你 船长 –谢谢船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Valar bless you, Captain. - Captain, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–维拉保佑你 –谢谢船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Valar bless you. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–谢谢船长 –谢谢船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, Captain. - Thank you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再吵就给你们好看 安静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you think this ends? Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–谢谢船长 谢谢 –维拉保佑你 船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, Captain. Thank you. - Bless you, Captain. Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–埃兰迪尔船长 –维拉保佑你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Captain, Elendil. - Valar bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蓝迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Valandil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我可以把你从名单中拿掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps I can have you taken off the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟国王谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll speak to the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意为了我这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是多年老友了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're one of my oldest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经表达得很清楚 你跟谁是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you've made it clear enough who your friends are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最尊贵的至高王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most noble High King.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅以此信表达我的喜悦之情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I write this letter to convey my deep joy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺三戒在林顿的完美成就\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on hearing of the success of the Three Rings in Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照要求 熔炉已灭 工坊已空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As requested, the forge is dark and the workshop is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城市弥漫着宝贵的宁静 我能预见光明的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A precious calm has settled over the city, and I foresee brighter days ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期盼您能尽快来访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you are able to make a visit soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.37,0:24:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时 我将一如既往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until then, I remain as ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忠实的随从 凯勒布林博领主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your loyal servant, Lord Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的大军已准备就绪 还在等什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our armada is ready to depart. What are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.04,0:24:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃瑞吉安一切安好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All is well in Eregion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这封信证明加拉德瑞尔是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The letter proves Galadriel was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.70,0:24:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们犹豫的同时 阿达尔的军队日益壮大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And whilst we hesitate, Adar's army grows stronger by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要进攻 现在就该出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we are to invade, we must leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.58,0:24:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人在魔多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy is in Mordor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.45,0:24:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真打算把中洲的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you truly prepared to wager the future of Middle-earth
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.29,0:24:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌在那枚戒指的低语上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the whispers of that Ring alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.33,0:24:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是你促成的 - 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You pushed for this. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–打从一开始 –没错 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- From the beginning. - I know. I did. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.00,0:25:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但学会倾听山脉的声音 是奥力的恩赐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But learning to hear the mountain's a gift from Aul?,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.16,0:25:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一辈子的千锤百炼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one that's honed and refined over a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.95,0:25:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this it...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像在作弊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It feels somehow like cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是都林三世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, he's Durin the Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对运用权力应该颇有心得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he knows a thing or two about wielding power.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.08,0:25:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种力量就连最善良的矮人 都会受到考验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That kind of power would test even the most virtuous of Dwarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.20,0:25:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷你父王能坚持正道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I pray your father keeps his path true.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.25,0:25:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.45,0:25:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你两百就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two hundred for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.12,0:25:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两百 就一块石头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two hundred? For a bloody rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.08,0:25:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是调音水晶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a tuning crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.16,0:25:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他什么神奇水晶 老子不付\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care if it's a cart and six horses. I won't pay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.91,0:25:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪国王的新法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, blame the king's new law.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每花一分钱 就要上缴一分钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For every coin spent, another goes to the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.87,0:26:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他称之为戒指税\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ring tribute, he calls it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.00,0:26:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指稅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ring tribute?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.87,0:26:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 这是我们女儿下周的生日礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, this is for our wee girl's birthday next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.16,0:26:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在她份上算便宜一点  我们出一百\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spare a bit for her sake? We'll give you 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.04,0:26:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–一百  –一百\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- One hundred? - One hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.37,0:26:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.37,0:26:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本是抢劫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like mine shaft robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.66,0:26:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–小心 –我的奥力啊 不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Careful. - Aul?'s beard, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.33,0:26:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–小心  –滚走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's rollin'. It's rollin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.62,0:26:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被你踢走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You seem to have kicked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.20,0:26:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士 真抱歉挡到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam, I'm so sorry to get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.20,0:26:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡到了...没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have it, I have it, I have it. Oof! No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.08,0:27:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.70,0:27:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小家伙 你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.08,0:27:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.25,0:27:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.75,0:27:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.20,0:28:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮人七大王国的各位使者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emissaries of the seven Dwarven realms,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.41,0:28:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天聚集大家在此 是因为中洲正在发生变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have gathered you all here today because Middle-earth is changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.66,0:28:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的四肢开始伸展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its limbs are stretching.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.12,0:28:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的骨头嘎吱作响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its bones, creaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.45,0:28:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种黑暗意志威胁着我们所有王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some dark will threatens all our kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.29,0:28:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在奥力的眷顾下 我的子民通过了考验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But by Aul?'s favor, my people have passed this test.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.00,0:28:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快你们的人民也会通过考验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And soon, yours shall pass it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.33,0:29:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一同迈向矮人的新时代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And rise together into a new age for our kind
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.75,0:29:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助一种将改变一切的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the help of a power that will change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.70,0:29:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七枚戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七名矮人国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.33,0:29:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一枚都蕴含着力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And bound within each... power.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.16,0:29:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌驾大地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Power over earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.08,0:29:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌驾岩石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Power over rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.16,0:29:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底改造矮人命运的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Power to shape the destinies of all Dwarves forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.25,0:29:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指不是给你的 是给你的国王的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Rings are not for you, but for your masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.58,0:29:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去转告国王 每个王国都能享有这份恩赐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go back and tell them that each of your realms may share in this bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.83,0:29:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是有代价的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it comes with a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.87,0:30:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡扎督姆将不再匮乏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khazad-d?m shall never want again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.91,0:30:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金子就在我们的脚下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is gold right beneath us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.83,0:30:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要再挖深一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should be delving much deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.50,0:30:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些限制是谁规定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But who set these restrictions?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.04,0:30:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你规定的 陛下 数十年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you did, sire. Decades ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.95,0:30:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那删掉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then strike them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.75,0:30:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,删掉...可是 陛下...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strike... But, sire--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.79,0:30:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,删掉 采矿大师 不然我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strike them, Delve-master, or I'll find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.91,0:30:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–哪去了  –你拿下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where is it? - You took it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.66,0:30:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪去了 你把它怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is it? What have you done with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.45,0:30:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那 陛下 你拿下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's there, sire. You-- You took it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.08,0:30:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说觉得手有点重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said your hand was feeling heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.87,0:30:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was. It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.87,0:31:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始挖吧 我做记号的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Start to dig, points where I've marked.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.62,0:31:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.25,0:31:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.75,0:31:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矿石下面有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's something under the mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.20,0:31:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莎亲耳听到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disa heard it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.37,0:31:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个未知的邪魔 古老而强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A nameless evil, ancient and powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.62,0:31:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能挖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mustn't dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.75,0:31:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到命令了 采矿大师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have your orders, Delve-master.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.58,0:31:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳维 我求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Narvi, I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.95,0:31:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采矿大师 你听到命令了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Delve-master. You have your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.66,0:32:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石之歌者说听到山脉的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stone-singers speak of hearing the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.62,0:32:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–什么  –这枚戒指能让我看到景象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - With this Ring, I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.04,0:32:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个矿井 每块矿石 每颗宝石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every shaft, every ore, every jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.33,0:32:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几千年来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.54,0:32:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们挖取的 不过是那浩瀚矿海的九牛一毛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have barely taken a thimble from the ocean of her riches.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.41,0:32:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莎搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disa is mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.62,0:32:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.45,0:32:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 大人 - 怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My lord. - Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.87,0:32:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.66,0:32:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.50,0:33:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛蒙蔽了我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do my eyes deceive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.45,0:33:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在铸造新样式的戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were casting a new design for a Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.04,0:33:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米尔妲妮亚试着调整大小时...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mirdania was attempting to resize it when...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.87,0:33:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.66,0:33:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–小心  –大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look out! - Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.62,0:33:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.75,0:33:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.00,0:34:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.00,0:34:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.25,0:34:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚在一个像这里的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was in a place like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.66,0:34:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是笼罩在迷雾和黑暗之中...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but shrouded in mist and darkness, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到...我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw-- I--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.04,0:34:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我以为是熔炉起火了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At first, I thought it was the forge burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.87,0:34:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.70,0:34:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.00,0:34:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很高大...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.45,0:34:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤由烈焰构成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and its skin was made of flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.33,0:34:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它朝我走来 呼着气 散发着死亡的气息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It came toward me, breathing, reeking of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.08,0:34:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到...我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I saw... I--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.12,0:34:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到它的眼神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw its eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.33,0:34:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无情且深远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pitiless and eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.66,0:35:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一直在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.25,0:35:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一直以来都在我们身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's been here among us, all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.66,0:35:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在跟我们在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are with us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.66,0:35:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好害怕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.95,0:35:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看四周\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.66,0:35:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.20,0:35:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这次做了什么改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you do differently this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.95,0:35:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赠礼之主跟你一样担心 人类太容易腐化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Lord of Gifts shared your worry that Men are too corruptible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.33,0:35:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们尝试添加更多秘银 来强化合金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, we sought to fortify the alloy by adding more mithril.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.33,0:35:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.66,0:35:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 你们应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you'd wanted to do that, you should've...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.95,0:35:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.79,0:35:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以少走很多弯路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would save us immeasurable hours of toil
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.25,0:35:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你愿意给我们一点点建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you would offer this one, single word of counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.91,0:36:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–凯勒布林博大人 –你们应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My lord, Celebrimbor. - You should--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.12,0:36:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人 抱歉打扰 都林王子从卡扎督姆过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, my lord, but Durin the Younger is arrived from Khazad-d?m.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.79,0:36:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, tell him to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.00,0:36:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说有急事 跟戒指有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He says it is urgent. Something about the Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.25,0:36:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看他想做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will see what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.66,0:36:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.41,0:36:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.08,0:36:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说“变了”是指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you mean "changed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.20,0:36:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他变得更加冷血 更加暴躁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like he's colder. Quicker to anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.08,0:36:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说他拒绝分享其他戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now they tell me, he refuses to share the other Rings
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.04,0:36:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非该国国王答应给他一半矿产\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless the Dwarf-lords promise him half a share of their mines!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.83,0:36:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一向不是贪婪之人 从来都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, greed is not his way. It never has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.66,0:36:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.08,0:37:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有可能他戴的戒指...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it possible the Ring he's wearing--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.20,0:37:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.16,0:37:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们采用跟三戒同样的工序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We used the same process, Durin,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.62,0:37:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的材料 甚至同样的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the same materials, even the same tools as for the Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.87,0:37:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的戒指不可能出错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, there simply cannot be a fault in your Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.41,0:37:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那或许出错的是铸戒人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then maybe, the fault's in the Ring-maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.41,0:37:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.58,0:37:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对这位安那塔了解多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much do you really know about this Annatar?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.79,0:37:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.45,0:37:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦见过不可见世界 有些人再也无法融入这个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some who behold the Unseen world are never quite at home in this one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.04,0:37:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.70,0:38:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.87,0:38:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它的光芒映照下 万物显现出最真实的样貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In its light, things appear as they truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.37,0:38:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影各异的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beings of differing shades of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.91,0:38:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And its darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.37,0:38:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很痛心地说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It pains me to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.20,0:38:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所看到的 我不希望你们任何人看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for what you saw, I did not wish for any of you to see
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.04,0:38:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我帮助他痊愈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until I had helped him to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.29,0:38:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你是说凯勒布林博大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You... You speak of... Lord Celebrimbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.75,0:38:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.25,0:38:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锻造三戒和七戒的过程中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The toll that creation has exacted from him
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.16,0:38:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他耗损太多 变得太虚弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in crafting the Three and the Seven has left him diminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.70,0:38:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,易受魔影侵害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vulnerable to the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.54,0:38:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我看到的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, what I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.45,0:38:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我你不会说出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise me you'll speak to none other of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.50,0:38:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括他本人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Including him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.87,0:39:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.45,0:39:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.50,0:39:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当阳光照在你的头发上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the light caught your hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.29,0:39:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么一瞬间 你看起来跟她一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for a moment, you seemed her perfect likeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.70,0:39:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟谁一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose likeness?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.50,0:39:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是加拉德瑞尔夫人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why, Lady Galadriel's, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.00,0:39:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些逝去的灵魂渴望平静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The souls of those we have lost yearn for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.58,0:39:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我们将协助他们安息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tonight, we will help them to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.95,0:39:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将在遥远的绿色国度再次相聚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until we meet again in the far green country
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.16,0:39:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冉冉升起的朝阳之下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}under a swift sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.58,0:40:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王下令封闭这座神殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This shrine is condemned by order of the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.91,0:40:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都回家去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Return to your homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.16,0:40:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 这是努门诺尔最古老的神殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My son, this is the oldest shrine in Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.62,0:40:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它挡到了新水道的去路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's in the way of the new aqueduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.08,0:40:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行离开 否则将强制驱离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave willingly or leave by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.41,0:40:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王表达他的歉意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The King sends his apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.83,0:41:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿以你为耻是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's it feel to have a daughter who's ashamed of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.45,0:41:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.62,0:41:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到他说的了 老头 出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You heard him, old man. Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.33,0:41:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.79,0:41:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.33,0:41:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我护送他出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll escort him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.79,0:41:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如果没被安放好 她为之哭泣的灵魂就会消散\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she is not stored, the souls for whom she weeps will be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.95,0:41:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把圣物给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give him the relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.41,0:41:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他 小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give it to him, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.33,0:42:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得你知不知道 我已晋升为...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know if you're aware, but I've been promoted to--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.79,0:42:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.00,0:42:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座神殿是忠贞派的圣地 不欢迎国王的走狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This shrine is for The Faithful. King's men aren't welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.70,0:42:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到你在祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't see you praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.91,0:42:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–愿维拉宽恕我 –宽恕你什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- May the Valar forgive me. - For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.95,0:42:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.70,0:42:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.91,0:42:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蓝迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Valandil!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.29,0:43:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 维蓝迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Valandil!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.58,0:43:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.08,0:43:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 维蓝迪尔 放下武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Valandil, put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.37,0:43:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put it down, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.37,0:43:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.62,0:44:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命 船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.58,0:44:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.75,0:44:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.20,0:44:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.33,0:45:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.83,0:45:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.16,0:45:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知狱卒是他发起暴动的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inform the jailer he was the one who started the uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.25,0:45:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我告诉你 矮人戒指有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! No, I tell you there is something wrong with the Dwarven Rings!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.12,0:45:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能都林国王自己滥用戒指 想推卸责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or King Durin is misusing his Ring and seeking to deflect blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.66,0:45:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.45,0:45:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I do not believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.04,0:46:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为能够巧妙操控金属的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As one who so masterfully manipulates metals,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.66,0:46:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心有没有人试图操控你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just be mindful someone is not manipulating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.12,0:46:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是幻想匕首的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see daggers where there are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.87,0:46:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却视而不见 直到匕首抵住你的喉咙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you ignore them, until they are right at your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.25,0:46:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.00,0:46:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.00,0:46:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某种程度上...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in some way...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.29,0:46:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在矮人戒指上动了手脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}alter the Dwarven Rings, yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.54,0:46:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.95,0:46:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.83,0:46:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.83,0:46:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是精神层面的关系 就跟工艺一样关键\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These are matters of spirit, as much as craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.37,0:47:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次过程中蕴藏了欺骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this time, we brought deceit into the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.45,0:47:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deceit?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.91,0:47:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么欺骗...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What deceit could you poss--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.83,0:47:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.62,0:47:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.45,0:47:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 那只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.33,0:47:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒谎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.29,0:47:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是撒谎 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was not a lie. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.00,0:47:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的至高王同意锻造精灵三戒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your High King consented to the Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.33,0:47:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但矮人七戒 是在欺骗之下锻造出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the Seven we forged beneath a cloak of deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.00,0:47:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须立刻前往林顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must go to Lindon forthwith,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.54,0:47:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的至高王坦白真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and confess the truth to your High King.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.41,0:47:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然情况会更糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or matters will worsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.08,0:47:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这样他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, do that, he would...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.91,0:47:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会再同意我锻造任何东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He would never permit me to forge anything again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.45,0:47:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is either that,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.12,0:47:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会陷入...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or we plunge straight on...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.54,0:47:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更深的漩涡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even deeper into the maelstrom.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.25,0:48:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王 我去了埃瑞吉安一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father, I have been to Eregion.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.29,0:48:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 这些戒指 肯定沾染了邪恶气息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tell you, some devilry has gone into these Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.41,0:48:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再使用它们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We mustn't use them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.00,0:48:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间和压力可以塑造矮人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time and pressure can shape a Dwarf,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.62,0:48:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同塑造岩石一般\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as surely as it can shape a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.75,0:48:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本希望你我的疏离 有助于塑造你 我儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had hoped our estrangement would help shape you, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.08,0:48:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我没想到这对我的影响这么大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I did not expect how much it would shape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.91,0:48:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–父王... –我以你为荣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Father-- - I am proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.66,0:48:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–不 –我以你为荣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - I am proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.83,0:48:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想与精灵合作的渴望 拯救了我们王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your desire to partner with the Elves has saved our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.70,0:48:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 现在 比起以往任何时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why now, now, more than ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.75,0:48:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.37,0:48:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的斧头在我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need your axe, by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.08,0:49:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林王子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prince Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.16,0:49:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.37,0:49:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林 他怎么说 他有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin, what did he say? Did he--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.12,0:49:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.12,0:49:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–可是... –都林 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But-- - Durin, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.70,0:49:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着告诉他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tried to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.95,0:49:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.66,0:49:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.25,0:50:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓你永远不会戴上那戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swear to me that you will never wear one of those Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.75,0:50:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.91,0:50:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩石和矿石深处 蕴藏着不可思议的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is agency uncanny in the heart of stone and ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.04,0:50:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作品尚未成形之时 就已开始...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even when a work is yet within the artist's bosom, it begins to...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.33,0:50:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心生违逆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}disobey him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.87,0:50:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们失败了 我们每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have failed. Every one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.04,0:50:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人 锻造过程相当精确严谨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The designs were carried out to the most exacting detail, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.75,0:50:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.45,0:50:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一次敲击都完美无缺吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every last hammer stroke done to perfection?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.83,0:50:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是傲慢和怠惰 让你们的注意力变得迟钝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or did, did hubris and sloth come together to dull your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.12,0:51:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个方式能弥补我们的错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must atone for our mistakes in the only way we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.29,0:51:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起完成所有力量之戒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by completing the Rings together.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.62,0:51:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类九戒的威力 必须不只为人类提供援助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Nine must do far more than bring aid to Men,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.08,0:51:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还必须为所有力量之戒带来平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they must bring balance to the entire project.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.20,0:51:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从精灵三戒汲取力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must draw strength from the Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.62,0:51:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以某种方式...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.29,0:51:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救赎矮人七戒的不足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}redeem the Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.95,0:51:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救赎我们大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must redeem us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.20,0:51:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要日夜赶工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We shall work night and day.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.16,0:51:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新设计 新合金 新工序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New designs. New alloys. A new process.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.62,0:51:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会时刻与大家同在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will be with you at every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.33,0:51:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们当中任何人 只要有一丝一毫的懈怠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And any of you who offers so much as a hair's breadth less
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.75,0:51:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都将不再有资格...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than his utmost effort is a s--
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.16,0:52:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以埃瑞吉安工匠自居\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A smith of Eregion no longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.45,0:52:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的够清楚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have I made myself plain?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.00,0:52:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚 大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, yes, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.54,0:52:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.66,0:52:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What has gotten into him?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.33,0:52:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位朋友 不要气馁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friends. Do not be discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.29,0:52:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们大人可能看来不可理喻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your master may seem unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.83,0:52:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求太过苛刻 甚至是不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His demands intemperate, or even impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.00,0:52:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是因为他清楚知道 你们的成功有多么重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that is simply because he knows how much depends on your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.37,0:52:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们不会让他失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet, I know you will not disappoint him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.04,0:52:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.20,0:52:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I, for one, am certain
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.25,0:52:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定能完成力量之戒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we will complete the Rings of Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.37,0:52:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.75,0:53:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.95,0:53:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, of course, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.79,0:53:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是赠礼之主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord of Gifts indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.62,0:53:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动工吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.87,0:54:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}High King!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.58,0:54:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 奥克不在魔多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}High King, the Orcs are not in Mordor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.08,0:54:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一支奥克大军往埃瑞吉安去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A legion of them are headed for Eregion.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.83,0:54:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.04,0:54:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要马上派兵前往埃瑞吉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must send the army to Eregion this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.37,0:54:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That will not be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.54,0:54:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有理由相信是索隆策划了这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have reason to believe that Sauron is the architect of all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.16,0:54:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 埃瑞吉安是精灵王国的宝石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}High King, Eregion is the very jewel of Elvendom.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.25,0:54:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦沦陷 对整个中洲会是致命的打击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it were to fall, it would be a mortal blow for all in Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.41,0:54:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要派兵援助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must send aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.20,0:54:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的军队 无法同时打败阿达尔和索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our armies cannot defeat both Adar and Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.33,0:54:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单凭一己之力不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.83,0:54:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.95,0:54:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back away!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.66,0:55:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.41,0:55:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.20,0:55:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–小心她 –没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look out for her. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.29,0:55:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.91,0:55:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I brought you here
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.12,0:55:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是把你当囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not as a prisoner...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.95,0:55:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是可能的盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But as a potential ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.79,0:56:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们有共同的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For we share a common enemy.

